    "en": {
      "title": "Five more people died due to corona infection in the country",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Yesterday (25.07.2022) 05 more people died due to corona infection in the country, Government Information Department informed.",
        "In that way, five people including three men and two women over the age of 60 have died.",
        "Due to the rapid spread of corona virus again in the country, doctors have asked people to wear face masks and be very safe."
      ],
